NAME = Alive
GARNAME = alive
GARVERSION = 2.0.2
HOME_URL = http://www.gnu.org/software/alive/
DESCRIPTION = Autologin and keep-alive daemon
define BLURB
GNU Alive sends periodic pings to a server, generally to keep a
connection alive.
endef

